name: I-Kebana #2 Valentine
description: I-Kebana Valentine, special edition # HEN200 Inspired by the Japanese art of arranging flowers with roots in Zen Buddhism and a reverence for nature, the tradition has become both a philosophy and an art. The artwork features stylized 3D plants that take Ikebana into a contemporary context, experimenting with new forms and processes with an emphasis on metacosmic structures.
